    code element (rivaroxaban = 1114195). Adapter must walk one level
    deep to find it — top-level text-only matching would miss this.
  - Mixed med list: rivaroxaban (anticoag, code-coded), Albuterol (inhaler,
    not anticoag, free text), and "Xarelto 20mg" brand name (would also
    trigger via substring channel — but RxNorm channel hits first).
